   <mods:abstract>Writes from Bedford. Visited Mrs. McVickar. Met newlyweds -- a bride 32
            years her husband's junior. Jay's friends in Bedford anxious to see him in May. John and
            James Randall's financial problems. Establishment of Sunday Schools at Episcopal
            churches of Westchester. Bishop supports the move. Mr. Milner's sermon. Kearney doing
            well at Eastchester church</mods:abstract>
